{"id":155952,"date":[{"year":1949,"month":7,"day":17}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"人民美术","column":"","genre":"","count":"174","ytitle":"","mtitle":"地下英雄的故事","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>企美</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060701.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>企美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)边美棠被派到城市里去工作，在路上有二个汉子在后面跟着他。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060702.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(二)到了家以后，那二个汉子忽然不见了。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060703.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(三)在当天的深夜，边美棠就被三个便衣抓了去。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060704.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(四)他被拖进了城外一个碉堡里。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060705.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(五)严刑逼供，百般拷打，边美棠一字不供。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\07\\497h060706.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(六)匪特们得到上峰犒赏袁洋廿块，就用刺刀戳死了辽美棠，当他临刑喊出了“中国共产党万岁”后就成了仁。</FONT>"}]}